						<summary>

						<p>Slab in the field of the village Paṭēl.</p>						

						<p><hi rend="bold">14th century A.D.</hi></p>						

						<p>This badly damaged record seems to registers a grant made by a person named Timmaya. </p>						

						<p>It is dated in the cyclic year Durmukhi, Jēshṭa, ba. 30. The cyclic year Durmukhi occurred twice during the 15th century <hi rend="italic">viz.,</hi> Śaka 1338 1416 A.D., and Śaka 1398 1476 A.D.</p>						

						</summary>
